                    <h2><a href='http://www.tweaking4all.com/news/applepi-baker-v1-5-update/'>ApplePi-Baker v1.5 update</a></h2>
                </div> 
                
                <div class="t4a_post_image t4a_link_noborder">
                	<img src="http://www.tweaking4all.com/wp-content/themes/tweaking4all/css/images/featured_image_news.png" alt="ApplePi-Baker v1.5 update" width="180" height="151"/><ul><li style="color:#444"><i class="icon-user"></i><ul><li title="Level of Difficulty - <strong>Not applicable</strong> - Super easy or just information."><i class="icon-star-empty"></i><i class="icon-star-empty"></i><i class="icon-star-empty"></i></li></ul></li></ul>                    
                    
                    
					                    <ul><li><i class="icon-folder-close-alt">
                    	</i> 
                            <ul>
                            	<li><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/category/news/" title="<i class='icon-folder-close-alt'> News &amp; Updates - View all articles in this Category">News &amp; Updates</a></li>                            </ul>
