                    </div>
                	<p>Available as of today, version 1.4.2 of <a title="TV Series - Rename your TV Series Files" href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/home-theatre/rename-your-tv-series-files/">Name My TV Series</a>, for Windows, MacOS X and Linux (32bit and 64bit).</p>
