<li id="random_links-2" class="widget "><h2 class="widgettitle">Interesting Links</h2>
<ul><li><i class="icon-link"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://winscp.net/" target="_blank">http://winscp.net/</a><br><span>WinSCP - Great free tool for (S)FTP/SSH, includes remote editing of text files, copying files, etc.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-link"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://xbmc.org/" target="_blank">XBMC</a><br><span>XBMC is probably the best media center application out there, suitable for multiple platforms.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-link"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://mariusth.heliohost.org/vimediamanager/" target="_blank">ViMediaManager</a><br><span>ViMediaManager is a media manager for Mac OS X, allowing you to gather, store, and manage information, extra art, trailers and television tunes for your movie, television etc for use with for example XBMC.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-link"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="https://www.lpfrg.com/" target="_blank">Leapfrog 3D printers</a><br><span>Manufacturer of the great Creatr and Xeed 3D printers - Stunning customer service!!</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-link"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.speedtest.net/" target="_blank">SpeedTest.net</a><br><span>Test the speed of your Internet connection (requires Flash!!!)</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-lightbulb"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/favorite-links/">Links Page</a><br><span>These and more of our favorite links can be found on the Links Page.</span></li></ul></li>
<li id="recent_downloads-2" class="widget "><h2 class="widgettitle">New Downloads</h2>
<ul><li><i class="icon-save"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/downloads/burningtools/Universal-USB-Installer-1.9.5.4.exe" target="_blank" title="<i class='icon-download'></i> Universal-USB-Installer-1.9.5.4.exe - Click here to download this file - Counted Downloads: 8">Universal-USB-Installer</a><br><span>Universal USB Installer a Windows application that allows you to choose from a selection of Linux Distributions (ISO) to create a bootable USB drive.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-save"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/downloads/qnap/SickRage.qpkg" target="_blank" title="<i class='icon-download'></i> SickRage.qpkg - Click here to download this file - Counted Downloads: 31">SickRage</a><br><span>SickRage, or SickBeard-TVRage, is a SickBeard fork, offering a lot of neat features SickBeard lacks, and automates the download of TV-Series through NZB (Usenet) of Torrents. This is a QPKG package for QNAP NAS Devices (tested on Intel).</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-save"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/downloads/arduino/T4A_Temperature_Drone_push.zip" target="_blank" title="<i class='icon-download'></i> T4A_Temperature_Drone_push.zip - Click here to download this file - Counted Downloads: 98">T4A Temperature Drone (Push)</a><br><span>Example Arduino Sketch (.ino) and PHP files to push data from an Arduino over Ethernet to a web-server.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-save"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/downloads/raspberrypi/ApplePi-Baker.zip" target="_blank" title="<i class='icon-download'></i> ApplePi-Baker.zip - Click here to download this file - Counted Downloads: 2746">ApplePi-Baker</a><br><span>ApplePi-Baker is a free application to flash SD-Cards for Raspberry Pi use. It can flash IMG files, and create SD-Cards for NOOBS use. This is the most recent version.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-save"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/downloads/network/DD-WRT%20R7000%20Kong%2024200.zip" target="_blank" title="<i class='icon-download'></i> DD-WRT R7000 Kong 24200.zip - Click here to download this file - Counted Downloads: 155">DD-WRT NetGear R7000</a><br><span>DD-WRT Firmware for a NetGear R7000 Nighthawk Wi-Fi router. We highly recommend looking at http://www.myopenrouter.com for the most recent version.</span></span></li><li><i class="icon-lightbulb"></i> <span class="t4a_sidebar_link"><a href="http://www.tweaking4all.com/downloads/">Downloads Page</a><br><span>Find these and more Downloads on the Downloads Page, where you will also find articles references, operating system requirements and categories.</span></li></ul></li>
        
        
